      "unit_id": "p19_g07",
      "translation": "The Board recommends an increase in the final dividend of 7.5% to 100.30 Hong Kong cents per share, subject to approval by shareholders at the Company's forthcoming Annual General Meeting. This brings the total dividend for 2020 to 135.30 Hong Kong cents per share, representing an increase of 6.9% compared to the total dividend for 2019. This reflects AIA's long-established prudent, sustainable and progressive dividend policy, which enables the Group to capitalize on future growth opportunities while maintaining financial flexibility."
